isFrozen\"><code>Object.isFrozen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isSealed\"><code>Object.isSealed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys\"><code>Object.keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/seal\"><code>Object.seal()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/values\"><code>Object.values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Określa funkcję tworzącą prototyp obiektu. Należy pamiętać, że wartość tej własności jest referencją do funkcji, a nie łańcuchem znaków zawierającym jej nazwę.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wszystkie obiekty dziedziczą własność <code>constructor</code> z ich prototypu (<code>prototype</code>):</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> o <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\no<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>constructor <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>constructor <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Array<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>constructor <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_wy.c5.9bwietlanie_konstruktora_obiektu","title":"Przykład: Wyświetlanie konstruktora obiektu","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniższy przykład tworzy prototyp, <code>Drzewo</code> i obiekt tego typu <code>sosna</code>. Następnie wyświetlana jest własność <code>constructor</code> obiektu <code>Drzewo</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Drzewo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nazwa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nazwa<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>nazwa<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nsosna <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Drzewo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sosna\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sosna.constructor to \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> sosna<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>constructor<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Przykład ten wyświetla:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">sosna.constructor to function Drzewo(nazwa) {\n   this.nazwa = nazwa;\n}\n</pre>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"}],"summary":"Określa funkcję tworzącą prototyp obiektu. Należy pamiętać, że wartość tej własności jest referencją do funkcji, a nie łańcuchem znaków zawierającym jej nazwę.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Object.prototype.constructor","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/constructor","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/constructor/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Dokumentacja referencyjna JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Obiekty"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object","title":"Object"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor","title":"Object.prototype.constructor"}],"pageTitle":"Object.prototype.constructor - Jav